Class SeleniumActionFunctions

  • java.lang.Object
    • finalAutomation.SeleniumActionFunctions
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DriverScript

    public class SeleniumActionFunctions
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains functions to perform all the Selenium actions. These actions include opening a URL in a browser, clicking elements, selecting an element, and sending values to textboxes.
    Author:
    Mehak Bains
